NK033(gi)002:1: // rdzogs pa chen po klong sde rdo rje zam pa'i bla brgyud gsol 'debs ni /
NK033(gi)002:2: thog ma'i sangs rgyas kun bzang rdo rje sems //
NK033(gi)002:3: sems dag nor bu dga' rab rdo rje dang //
NK033(gi)002:4: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen sh+r+ai sid+ha la //
NK033(gi)002:5: gsol ba 'debs so bdag rgyud byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)002:6: bee ro tsa na spang ston mi pham mgon //
NK033(gi)002:7: ngan lam byang rgyal za ngam rin chen dbyig /
NK033(gi)002:8: khu 'gyur gsal mchog nyang ston byang chub grags //
NK033(gi)002:9: gsol ba shes rab 'byung gnas rba sgom ye shes mtshan //
NK033(gi)002:10: d+harma bo d+hi 'dzeng dkar jo sras dang //
NK033(gi)002:11: kun bzang rdo rje sangs rgyas sdong po la //
NK033(gi)002:12: gsol ba ye shes byang chub ye shes dbang po dang //
NK033(gi)002:13: ngur ston bsod 'od rdo rje dbang phyug zhabs //
NK033(gi)002:14: bsod nams rgyal mtshan shes rab rgyal mtshan la //
NK033(gi)002:15: gsol ba gzhon nu shes rab gzhon nu grags pa dang //
NK033(gi)002:16: sangs rgyas bzang po brtson 'grus dbang phyug zhabs //
NK033(gi)002:17: mtha' bzhi grags rin sh+aakya rgyal po la //
NK033(gi)002:18: gsol ba 'gos lo gzhon dpal spyan snga chos kyi grags //
NK033(gi)002:19: chos kyi blo gros khyung tshang blo gros dpal //
NK033(gi)002:20: karma gu ru chos dbang lhun grub la //
NK033(gi)002:21: gsol ba chos dbang kun bzang kun bzang chos kyi rgyal //
NK033(gi)002:22: 'gyur med rdo rje rin chen rnam rgyal dang //
NK033(gi)002:23: pad+ma bstan 'dzin o d+ai ya na la //
NK033(gi)002:24: gsol ba rig 'dzin bzang po pad+ma mang+ga la //
NK033(gi)002:25: rig pa'i rdo rje 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang //
NK033(gi)002:26: nges don dbang po rtsa brgyad bla ma la /
NK033(gi)002:27: gsol ba 'debs so bdag rgyud byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)002:28: rang sems gsal stong 'dzin med rtogs pa dang //
NK033(gi)002:29: yul kun snang stong bden med 'char ba dang //
NK033(gi)002:30: spangs blangs yongs bral 'khor 'das 'khrul pa zhig /
NK033(gi)002:31: gnyug ma'i gtan sa zin par byin gyis rlobs //
NK033(gi)002:32: zhes snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i bla brgyud gsol
NK033(gi)002:33: 'debs gter chen 'gyur med rdo rje'i gsung la gter
